    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61001005-61001007",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>信徒最終應該藉著信心獲得什麼？  </strong></p><p>藉著信心，他們最終應該獲得愛。</p>",
