    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>屬靈瞎眼的人忘記了什麼？  </strong></p><p>他忘記了從前罪惡得潔淨的事。</p>",
