    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "61003003-61003004",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>在末世，好譏</strong><span><strong>誚</strong></span><strong>的人會說什麼？</strong></p><p>好譏<span>誚</span>的人會質疑耶穌再來的應許，並且說自創造以來，一切都如同起初一樣。</p>",
